The exotic Mövenpick Hotel Ibn Battuta Gate is a Moroccan themed, 5-star hotel. We are looking for an AV technician to join the team.
This individual would fully understand the requirements in setting up audio and video equipment and will ensure cleanliness of work areas when executing requests to ensure guest satisfaction.
